<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.1.3/css/bootstrap.min.css"
        integrity="sha384-MCw98/SFnGE8fJT3GXwEOngsV7Zt27NXFoaoApmYm81iuXoPkFOJwJ8ERdknLPMO" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script defer src="https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.5.0/js/all.js"
        integrity="sha384-GqVMZRt5Gn7tB9D9q7ONtcp4gtHIUEW/yG7h98J7IpE3kpi+srfFyyB/04OV6pG0"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Open+Sans:300,300i,400,400i,700,700i" rel="stylesheet">
    <title>Welcome</title>
</head>
<style>
    * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {

        min-height: 100vh;
        background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3)), url(/back.png);
        font-family: sans-serif;
    }

    .row {
        max-width: 700px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .heading {
        margin: auto;
        padding: 50px 0;
        text-align: center;
        color: white;

    }

    .instructions {
        margin-left: 76px;
    }

    .para {
        color: white;
    }

    .button {
        margin: auto;
        text-align: center;
        padding-top: 50px;
    }

    .btn-form {
        margin: auto;
        padding-top: 20px;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .punch {
        color: white;
    }

    .error {
        color: red;
        text-align: center;
        margin: 10px auto auto auto;
    }

    .row1 {
        max-width: 700px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: white;
    }
</style>

<body>
    <div class="row1">
        <div class="error">
            <p>
                <bold> Looks like you didn't provide correct informations...<br>Check the instructions and try again.
                </bold>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class=" instructions">
            <div class="heading">
                <h1>&mdash;&mdash;&nbsp;&nbsp;Instructions&nbsp;&nbsp;&mdash;&mdash;</h1>
            </div>
            <div class="para">
                <p>1. Please provide your Voter Name & Voter Number according to the Voter List. </p>
                <p>2. Place yor Adhar Number carefully while entering.</p>
                <p>3. Don't leave your information incomplete.</p>
                <p>4. Do not refresh the page while putting your vote.</p>
                <p>5. Place your vote carefully, this is an one time process so you won't be able to </p>
                <p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; cast your vote again.</p>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row button">
        <div class="punch">
            <p>We are glad to inform you that we respect your vote and privacy. So do not worry, A single vote matters
                to us. </p>
        </div>
        <form class="btn-form" action="/registration-page" method="POST">
            <button class="btn" type="submit">START</button>
        </form>
    </div>
</body>

</html>